{"tid":1816733,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府正籌備「香港獨立」意志萌芽後，第一個大型煙花","createTime":"2020-01-08T12:54:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T11:48:08.000Z","uid":52090,"like":92,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"b101676e62c4f7b1abeccf3b4a7914cd1f5fcf10","tid":1816733,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T12:54:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">國慶、除夕煙花先後取消，今年大年初二，還會否有賀歲煙花？康文署指已經找了贊助商，籌備工作進行中，稍後公布詳情。<br />\n球迷最關心的賀歲盃亦未有定案，足總指下周二前才有決定，但就確認今年不會有外隊訪港。<br />\n球賽未知會否舉行 ，馬就會照跑，農曆新年賽馬日繼續在初三舉行。至於民間習俗，好像林村拋寶牒、黃大仙祠頭炷香都會如常舉行、嗇色園指保安措施會參考往年安排。<br />\n初二車公誕，鄉議局亦會繼續為香港求籤，鄕議局主席劉業強去年就為香港求得「家宅不吉」的中籤。<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/14912\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F14912&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IjYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=3a0bfbc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F14912&h=d8ab2e2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/14912</a></span><br />\n<br />\n當日一定好多中国旅客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同國際旅客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一齊想像當日情況<br />\n<br />\n應該會好多「口號師」，講出中英雙語嘅「口號」<br />\n仲會有大型「激光」表演，配合煙花<br />\n大廈外牆可能有「大型投影」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定好靚<br />\n<br />\n大家到時一定要齊齊去維港兩岸睇煙花 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"614e6c3405fa27562dfefce1f659132d2b3a2bf8","tid":1816733,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T12:54:59.000Z","msg":"借一借位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[黃色經濟圈再升級] 點解「少數親共派」可以壟斷商界聲音？就係因為冇人搞過黃色商會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1815638/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1815638/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[1分鐘懶人包] 功能組別&amp;選委會攻略網，小學生都識 (Plan B 戰線)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1813941/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1813941/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"ba9d9a9c84f5f952522e7cb97738e896bee45c49","tid":1816733,"uid":59297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T12:55:36.000Z","msg":"開年啦喂"},{"pid":"f7d14538e2d535c955e8005d398952bb331aed53","tid":1816733,"uid":30836,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T12:56:24.000Z","msg":"煙花咁嘈 會唔會乜都聽唔到"},{"pid":"3942b2919960f2196ac887cb654e9a98dc5c554e","tid":1816733,"uid":343712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T12:57:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ce8e7d4c56aba6393a460aeba47a7ef2bb1c69","tid":1816733,"uid":127469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T12:57:47.000Z","msg":"球迷最關心的賀歲盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d8e39e80d3de4c2348d02fd305c89d446d36a0d","tid":1816733,"uid":52090,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T12:59:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家新年會講咩祝賀說話？</span><br />\n<br />\n派利是比保安，唔好派錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e83c52ecd8dd25a0df6d0ffd0d051f1e0f1db41","tid":1816733,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T13:06:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0154227ac