sets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1137e492f8dd7c5f0a1cca26e77e82f07d0042e0","tid":1816733,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T14:25:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfca1fd6660e6c296fb63e50f08b46387e0e0430","tid":1816733,"uid":329448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b101676e62c4f7b1abeccf3b4a7914cd1f5fcf10","tid":1816733,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T12:54:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">國慶、除夕煙花先後取消，今年大年初二，還會否有賀歲煙花？康文署指已經找了贊助商，籌備工作進行中，稍後公布詳情。<br />\n球迷最關心的賀歲盃亦未有定案，足總指下周二前才有決定，但就確認今年不會有外隊訪港。<br />\n球賽未知會否舉行 ，馬就會照跑，農曆新年賽馬日繼續在初三舉行。至於民間習俗，好像林村拋寶牒、黃大仙祠頭炷香都會如常舉行、嗇色園指保安措施會參考往年安排。<br />\n初二車公誕，鄉議局亦會繼續為香港求籤，鄕議局主席劉業強去年就為香港求得「家宅不吉」的中籤。<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/14912\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F14912&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IjYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=3a0bfbc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F14912&h=d8ab2e2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/14912</a></span><br />\n<br />\n當日一定好多中国旅客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同國際旅客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一齊想像當日情況<br />\n<br />\n應該會好多「口號師」，講出中英雙語嘅「口號」<br />\n仲會有大型「激光」表演，配合煙花<br />\n大廈外牆可能有「大型投影」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定好靚<br />\n<br />\n大家到時一定要齊齊去維港兩岸睇煙花 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T14:34:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/c-7dcVw0VUY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fc-7dcVw0VUY&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IjYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=33f7c596\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.b